<title>Time table</title>
<body>

<p>
14 days for nominations and 14 days for voting:
</p>

<ul>
  <li>Nominations: 2014-06-14 00:00 UTC to 2014-06-27 23:59 UTC</li>
  <li>Voting: 2014-07-01 00:00 UTC to 2014-07-14 23:59 UTC</li>
</ul>

</body>
